{"prompt": "Generate a website for a community non-profit. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Connect</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* A lively red */\n            --secondary-color: #ffcdd2; /* A lighter, less contrasting red shade */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #f44336;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 0.75rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--accent-color) 100%);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 4rem 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n        }\n        .mission-section, .programs-section, .contact-section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .programs-section .program-item {\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n        .programs-section .program-item h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1rem 2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n                padding: 1.5rem;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 0.5rem 0;\n            }\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n            .hero-section p {\n                font-size: 1rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Community Connect</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#programs\">Our Programs</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <h2>Building a Stronger Tomorrow, Together.</h2>\n        <p>Join us in making a difference in our community through impactful initiatives and heartfelt support.</p>\n        <a href=\"#programs\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Work</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"mission-section\">\n            <h2>Our Mission</h2>\n            <p>At Community Connect, our mission is to foster a vibrant, inclusive, and supportive environment for everyone in our neighborhood. We believe in the power of collective action to address local challenges and create positive, lasting change.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"programs\" class=\"programs-section\">\n            <h2>What We Do</h2>\n            <div class=\"program-item\">\n                <h3>Youth Mentorship</h3>\n                <p>Empowering young minds with guidance, educational support, and opportunities for growth.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"program-item\">\n                <h3>Senior Support</h3>\n                <p>Providing companionship, essential resources, and activities to enhance the well-being of our elder community members.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"program-item\">\n                <h3>Local Events</h3>\n                <p>Organizing community gatherings, workshops, and celebrations that bring people together and strengthen local bonds.</p>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Volunteer With Us</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Have questions or want to get involved? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n            <p>Email: info@communityconnect.org</p>\n            <p>Phone: (123) 456-7890</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Community Connect. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}